cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is about person re-identification (Re-ID) which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a deep learning method for unsupervised Re-ID, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-category of machine learning, cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves tracking and spatio-temporal regularization, which could fall under the sub-categories of multimedia, cs.MM (Multimedia), artificial intelligence, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cryptography and security, cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
